            {
              "id": "lp2018_s1_comp_q1_prompt_1",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "Say whether the following statements are True or False? Write T or F next to the letter corresponding to the statement and correct the false one(s).\na) The Indus civilization was known before 1924.\nb) Sailors from Mesopotamia arrived at the Indus valley.\nc) The Indus valley cities and towns were well-protected.\nd) The Indus people's culture was not very developed."
            },
            {
              "id": "lp2018_s1_comp_q1_solution_1",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "a) F. The Indus civilization was not discovered until 1924.\nb) T\nc) T\nd) F. The Indus culture reached a fairly high level."
            },
            {
              "id": "lp2018_s1_comp_q1_rubric_1",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "2 pts: a) 0.75, b) 0.25, c) 0.25, d) 0.75"
